-hostage-release-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-2b4d-d0a5-abcf-3ffd183a0000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列预备役军人在加沙中部丧生，另一名士兵受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-29/ty-article/two-israeli-reservists-killed-in-central-gaza-another-soldier-seriously-wounded/0000018f-2b23-da33-a9cf-bb7749dd0000</link><description>军士长。 （研究）Ido Aviv，28 岁，军士长。 （修订案）军队称，37 岁的卡尔基丹·梅哈里 (Kalkidan Mehari) 在加沙地带的战斗中身亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 19:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-29/ty-article/two-israeli-reservists-killed-in-central-gaza-another-soldier-seriously-wounded/0000018f-2b23-da33-a9cf-bb7749dd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>